{"tid":2424715,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla , Ark ETF大跌 專家憂恐對市場造成漣漪效應","createTime":"2021-02-26T20:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T23:51:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e023c849664ec37b8022a6065539a4e4a4fee2b9","tid":2424715,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:28:25.000Z","msg":"在美國公債殖利率大幅上揚以及成長股受到衝擊下，部分避險基金經理已開始對那些先前流入特斯拉（TESLA）及方舟（ARK）基金等高漲股票的資金感到憂慮，本周方舟創新ETF及特斯拉跌幅超過12%。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》報導，在去年特斯拉等股票受到投資人大幅追捧下，使得「女股神」伍德（Cathie Wood）旗下規模266億美元的方舟創新ETF（ARK Innovation ETF）成為去年Morningstar追蹤數據中，表現最佳的主動型美股基金。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\nBortel Investment Management合夥人Peter Bortel表示，伍德操作非常高風險的投資組合，在特斯拉高點時馬上加碼特斯拉的行為「似乎有點不成熟」。<br />\n<br />\n根據路孚特數據，周一有4.65億美元資金從方舟創新ETF中撤離，若出現更多此類贖回，將導致方舟基金在平倉非流動資產前，在短期內賣出流動資產以應付擠兌。<br />\n<br />\nConnective Capital投資組合經理Rob Romero表示：「我擔心像ARK這類的基金可能被迫拋售，並對特定股票造成壓力，方舟是這些股票的大型持有者。」<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210227/XLUVNCKUO5CV3BBGKQ4UM4UIFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210227%2FXLUVNCKUO5CV3BBGKQ4UM4UIFU%2F&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B34IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=3891a24d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210227%2FXLUVNCKUO5CV3BBGKQ4UM4UIFU%2F&h=14707308\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210227/XLUVNCKUO5CV3BBGKQ4UM4UIFU/</a>"},{"pid":"b5fa6fc28986398d5018a9dfd11cf9a984b3c095","tid":2424715,"uid":37146,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:30:44.000Z","msg":"Cathie 都幾靚女"},{"pid":"7ec2600965d8bf1f021356a664ccffb9f4424bb3","tid":2424715,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5fa6fc28986398d5018a9dfd11cf9a984b3c095","tid":2424715,"uid":37146,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:30:44.000Z","msg":"Cathie 都幾靚女"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T20:40:32.